window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>The end of Nathan's struggle arrives as the immortal masterminds threatening his world show a personal interest.</b></p> <p>Demonic invasions ripple across the land, and Nathan questions if any moral line in the sand is worth the death of his loved ones. His years of preparation to save Doumahr may vanish overnight as he faces an onslaught intended to end everything.</p> <p>Where the goddess Omria failed time and time again over countless millennia to defeat her tormentors, Nathan must succeed. His second chance in life burns in front of his eyes. There won't be a third. Nathan will either defend his home, or he won't have one.</p> <p>In the end, is it truly heresy if nobody is left to judge him for it?</p>"; 
